General.Name: El Maniel International Inc
General.Description: El Maniel International, Inc., a development stage company, develops mining projects. El Maniel International, Inc. focuses on gold deposits in Ghana, West Africa and Papua New Guinea, Australasia. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in New York, New York. El Maniel International, Inc. is a subsidiary of Co-Max International Ltd.
